Subject: Re: [T2] Valve questions.........

Disconnect the spark, remove the valve cover and have someone crank it. 

Use a hose (heater hose, water hose) about 20" long and put one end to your ear and probe around the vavle train with the other. Should help pinpoint the noise. 

Prob the pushrod tube retainer spring. 

